#. Tag: date
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "2003-03-08"
msgstr "२००३-०३-०८"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<मन्वोल्नुम्>१</मन्वोल्नुम्>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "fool <command>make</command> into not rebuilding certain files"
msgstr ""
"fool <command>make</command> इत्यनेन कतिपयानां सञ्चिकानां पुनर्निर्माणं न करणीयम् इति"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>cheatmake</command> <group><option>hidechange</option> "
"<replaceable>file</replaceable></group> <group><option>show</option></group> "
"<group><option>why</option> <replaceable>file</replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>वञ्चना</command><group><option value=hidechange> hidechange इति</"
"option><replaceable> संचिका</replaceable></group><group><option value=show> "
"दर्शयतु</option></group><group><option value=why> किमर्थम्‌</option><replaceable> "
"संचिका</replaceable></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>cheatmake</command> is used to save time when recompiling. It can "
"fool make into skipping files that haven't changed in a meaningful way. This "
"can be used for instance when you change a comment in a file but none of the "
"actual code."
msgstr ""
"पुनः संकलनकाले समयस्य रक्षणार्थं <command>cheatmake</command> इत्यस्य उपयोगः भवति । "
"सार्थकरूपेण अपरिवर्तिताः सञ्चिकाः त्यक्तुं make मूर्खं कर्तुं शक्नोति । एतत् उदाहरणार्थं उपयोक्तुं "
"शक्यते यदा भवान् सञ्चिकायां टिप्पणीं परिवर्तयति परन्तु वास्तविकसङ्केतस्य कोऽपि न ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "एषा उपयोगिता &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर विकास किट।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: term
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>hidechange</option> <replaceable>file</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option value=hidechange>hidechange इति</option><replaceable> संचिका</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hides the fact that file was changed by setting the timestamp into the past. "
"Use with care!"
msgstr ""
"समयमुद्रिकां अतीते सेट् कृत्वा सञ्चिका परिवर्तिता इति तथ्यं गोपयति । सावधानीपूर्वकं प्रयोगं "
"कुर्वन्तु !"

#. Tag: option
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "show"
msgstr "दर्शयतु"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists what files <command>make</command> currently needs to rebuild"
msgstr ""
"<command>make</command> इत्यनेन सम्प्रति काः सञ्चिकाः पुनर्निर्माणस्य आवश्यकता अस्ति "
"इति सूचीं करोति"

#. Tag: term
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>why</option> <replaceable>file</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option value=why>किमर्थम्‌</option><replaceable> संचिका</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Explains why make must rebuild file"
msgstr "make must rebuild file इति किमर्थं व्याख्यायते"

#. Tag: title
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "पर्यावरणम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the following variables (but not both) should be set if the source "
"directory is different from the build directory. If the build directory is "
"simply a subdirectory of the source directory, the simpler variable "
"<envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> should be used."
msgstr ""
"यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका build निर्देशिकातः भिन्ना अस्ति तर्हि निम्नलिखितचरानाम् एकः (किन्तु "
"उभयत्र न) सेट् कर्तव्यः । यदि build निर्देशिका केवलं स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः उपनिर्देशिका अस्ति "
"तर्हि सरलतरं चरं <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> उपयोक्तव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: envar
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_SUBJDIR"
msgstr "OBJ_SUBJDIR"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indicates that the build directory is in the given subdirectory of the "
"source directory. For instance, if the source directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> and the build directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</"
"envar> should be set to <parameter>obj-i386-linux</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"build directory स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः दत्ते उपनिर्देशिकायां अस्ति इति सूचयति । यथा, यदि "
"स्रोतनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> अस्ति तथा च "
"निर्माणनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</"
"filename> अस्ति, तर्हि <envar> OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> इत्येतत् <parameter>obj-i386-"
"linux</parameter> इति सेट् कर्तव्यम् ।"

#. Tag: envar
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_REPLACEMENT"
msgstr "OBJ_REPLACEMENT इति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <command>sed</command> expression that is used to transform the source "
"directory into the build directory. For instance, if the source directory is "
"<filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then "
"<envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</envar> should be set to <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-"
"obj#</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"एकं <command>sed</command> व्यञ्जनं यत् स्रोतनिर्देशिकायाः निर्माणनिर्देशिकायां "
"परिवर्तनार्थं उपयुज्यते । यथा, यदि स्रोतनिर्देशिका <filename class=\"directory"
"\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename> अस्ति, तर्हि <envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</"
"envar> इति <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk- इति सेट् कर्तव्यम् । obj#</parameter> इति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-cheatmake.1.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "इदमपि पश्यन्तु"

